Summary: bright light in sky then rapid movement then appeared again, with another one a distance away
divs: Sighting Detailsgoing to bed i noticed aglow in the sky, it was cloudy but the light shone through the clouds, it was static for a few seconds then moved at speed out of view. after twenty seconds it appeared again in the same place, another one came a distance away,then both moved in different directions before appearing again. this went on for four times.
